summary: During the InnVestAI All Team Meeting, the team discussed the current accuracy rate of 95% and the need to address processing failures. There was a focus on understanding the existing processes that are in place to rectify these issues. The team emphasized the importance of improving accuracy and reducing failures in the system.

items.title: Review processing failure protocols
items.details: Investigate the current processes in place to address processing failures and identify areas for improvement. Acceptance criteria include a report outlining existing protocols and recommendations for enhancements.
